Recommande way:
To install Opencv for Windows please follow that link:
http://docs.opencv.org/3.1.0/d5/de5/tutorial_py_setup_in_windows.html

Esay way 1:
1. Install Anaconda from the official site:
   https://www.continuum.io/downloads/%E3%80%82

2. Run the installer and follow the instructions.

3. Open a cmd shell or a Anaconda shell.

4. Type conda install python-opencv or if it doesnt work try conda install opencv.

5. That should download opencv from the Anaconda cloud.

6. Navigate to your Anaconda folder and open python.exe.

7. Try to import cv2

8. If it work you are done

